e7a9117d012df4181e05de970f2210264b8685ee76c98b33795f8095d9a17b24b20e6ce920f944b4b5cb940cf672af5ba5fd0ffae9f53085a4f97da61b1e69f6  fix-crash-with-c-locale.patch"
